{"TopicId":221732,"ForumId":144,"TopicTitle":"Abrupt transition between the \u0022local space shadow\u0022 and the \u0022orbit shadow\u0022 (Very visible in canyons or craters)","CreatedByName":"Anonymous Bug Reporter","CreatedById":231013,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-22T10:04:47Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Anonymous Bug Reporter","CreatedById":231013,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-22T10:04:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0windows 11 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A05950x | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A04090 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E64G\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor craters below sea level, the lighting rendering of sunlight is incorrect and seems to be blocked, resulting in complete darkness\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-12-22T15:56:03Z\u0022 title=\u002212/22/2023 03:56  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Dec 22\u0022\u003EDecember 22, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by The Space Peacock\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stephensan","CreatedById":222320,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-04-10T14:10:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBug is still \u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:rgb(23,25,26);color:rgb(217,214,209);font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003Eoccurring\u003C/span\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anonymous Bug Reporter","CreatedById":231013,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-22T11:02:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0win10 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0i7- 7xxx | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0gtx1050ti | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E16gb\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyo big shadow dropping\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/cfield.php?storage=form_Fields\u0026amp;path=VID_20231222_120055.mp4\u0026amp;fileKey=%5B!AES128GCM%5BMrJrs/b%2BVSHEZkt5SqTuxNGUOYm5tdet9TnfAniwYdpIaBJKk8SvVoBTbQIVFGEp1szR1LVZqT%2BqlQvnJ9XeNHCFyWcKAstSs5uMIA==%5D%5Ba8de62a2c257962c72b639b4%5D%5Bfd184ae338b987fd41e8763b7a305b0e%5D%5D\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EVID_20231222_120055.mp4\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cvideo class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 controls=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.global.core.embeddedvideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Csource type=\u0022video/mp4\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/monthly_2023_12/VID_20231222_120055.mp4.8b05e4b6842c232d8ad286d57c4fa778.mp4\u0022\u003E\u003Ca class=\u0022ipsAttachLink\u0022 data-fileext=\u0022mp4\u0022 data-fileid=\u00221197\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/attachment.php?id=1197\u0026amp;key=c2e49af4d5a8afe912d3240f6baacee8\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EVID_20231222_120055.mp4\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/video\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-12-22T13:19:28Z\u0022 title=\u002212/22/2023 01:19  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Dec 22\u0022\u003EDecember 22, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Spicat\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spicat","CreatedById":228085,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-22T13:23:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe problem is from the shadow of the terrain that appear when you get close to it (a sort of LOD for the shadows), not from the craft, you can see this happening in craters but as well in canyons:\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://youtu.be/b8UomLV88GE?t=923\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://youtu.be/b8UomLV88GE?t=923\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GGzz12321","CreatedById":221199,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-23T12:03:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224350412\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022221732\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221703251383\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022228085\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spicat\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 hours ago, Spicat said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cfont\u003E\u95EE\u9898\u51FA\u5728\u4F60\u9760\u8FD1\u5730\u5F62\u65F6\u51FA\u73B0\u7684\u5730\u5F62\u9634\u5F71\uFF08\u4E00\u79CD\u9634\u5F71\u7684LOD\uFF09\uFF0C\u800C\u4E0D\u662F\u6765\u81EA\u98DE\u8239\uFF0C\u4F60\u53EF\u4EE5\u770B\u5230\u8FD9\u79CD\u60C5\u51B5\u53D1\u751F\u5728\u9668\u77F3\u5751\u4E2D\uFF0C\u4F46\u4E5F\u53D1\u751F\u5728\u5CE1\u8C37\u4E2D\uFF1A\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://youtu.be/b8UomLV88GE?t=923\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://youtu.be/b8UomLV88GE?t=923\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cfont\u003EYes, I have encountered the same issue as well\u003C/font\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002263R0MUe.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/63R0MUe.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022WtctBGv.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/WtctBGv.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the crater near the terminator zone, shadows cast by terrain features only appear within a certain range, making the lighting in the distance appear strange\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-26T18:01:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003ECustomFlags | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Win 10 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0i7-3770K | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0GTK 1060 6GB | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E32 GB\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt a normal zoom level (close to the Kerbal), the Minmus Monument is entirely hidden by a huge shadow:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00224GDzrgw.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022120.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/4GDzrgw.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf I zoom the camera out with the mouse wheel, the shadow starts to recede:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022qqFvo63.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022120.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/qqFvo63.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt about this distance, it\u0027s in full light:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00228K635dS.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022120.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/8K635dS.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe lighting should be independent of zoom level, and this statue in particular should be lit so players can see it and have the awe-inspiring moment that this must be intended to produce.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/cfield.php?storage=form_Fields\u0026amp;path=autosave_3.json\u0026amp;fileKey=[!AES128GCM[pbPAqn0K%2BCLWMgJ1VkInXEbaHPFULvM5voHQdc7Z7M%2BY8ZuLvQcCdF6WltH5iBfKK2oIVr/FIRxTZH9oiOySMg==][7a567f2a94d2b4e77fea8cee][9ba7829dfe20b038f54cb71c0dd8febc]]\u0022\u003Eautosave_3.json\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cstyle type=\u0022text/css\u0022\u003E\r\n.ipsImage {\r\nwidth: 900px !important;\r\n}\u003C/style\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spicat","CreatedById":228085,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-26T19:56:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/156657-hebarusan/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022156657\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/156657-hebarusan/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@HebaruSan\u003C/a\u003E, merged your bug report.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cocoscacao","CreatedById":225696,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-27T19:54:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.2.0 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 10 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0AMD Ryzen 9 5900x | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0AMD Radeon 6700 | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E32\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMonuments of ancients cast a shadow to the ground,\u003Cbr\u003E\nnot a single photon behind them, is there to be found.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTwo vessels and crews, on the journey did embark,\u003Cbr\u003E\nand somehow both of them, landed in the dark.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd yet, the panels didn\u0027t fail, the panels didn\u0027t cower,\u003Cbr\u003E\nfor even in the shadows, they produced the power.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EIncluded Attachments:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/applications/core/interface/file/cfield.php?storage=form_Fields\u0026amp;path=bug-minimus.json\u0026amp;fileKey=[!AES128GCM[Y5mZOIUUaJvbVMYWIJzV4eOSl%2BFIwhNDqBuRb2M9qjPpATRTdqxLgXlbsiECjC3WXFy%2BcdvalA7Z1Cb8Net6vLU=][40ba1d50015009cca90af86d][a8d1a12b31c2cb48a6884f1af59d8aa2]]\u0022\u003Ebug-minimus.json\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u